text: Manus District is a district of the Manus Province of Papua New Guinea. Its capital is Lorengau. The population of the district was 60,485 at the 2000 census.Districts of Papua New Guinea at statoids.com The district is composed strictly of Manus Island. ==References== Category:Districts of Papua New Guinea Category:Manus Province Category:Populated places in the Islands Region
title: Manus District
